    <p>
        <strong>Items We Cannot Clean</strong>
    </p>
    <p>Mold removal is a specialized service, and we cannot be liable for any mold-related risks in clients' homes. We also
        cannot clean hoarding homes or areas containing animal and human body fluids, blood, feces, vomit, cat litter boxes,
