    <p>
        <strong>Unreachable Areas &amp; Heavy items</strong>
    </p>
    <p>For safety and liability reasons, our providers cannot climb higher than a step stool or work outside your home.
        Additionally, cleaners cannot move objects weighing more than 35 pounds. If you need to clean behind heavy objects,
        please move them before our cleaners arrive.</p>
    <p>
        <strong>Breakage/Damage &amp; Loss Policy</strong>
    </p>
