    </p>
    <p>
        <strong>Rate Adjustments</strong>
    </p>
    <p>Rate adjustments may be made at any time if changes occur in the frequency of scheduled services, home, or living
        situation (e.g., remodel, change of address, number of people in the home, significant addition of furniture). Any
        annual rate increase will not exceed 10% of the client's current rate.</p>
    <p>
        <strong>Lockouts</strong>
    </p>
    <p>To ensure smooth service, please make sure to provide access to our cleaning providers on the scheduled service day.
        If our team is locked out, we will make every effort to contact you to arrange entry. If we cannot reach you within 30
        minutes of arrival, the scheduled cleaning will be skipped, and you will be charged the full value of the cleaning.</p>
    <p>
        <strong>Alarm</strong>
    </p>
    <p>If your home has a security system, please ensure it is off or provide us with the code and usage instructions.
